title: UFOs & Nukes - Coast to Coast april 24, 2016
description:
UFOs & Nukes

Coast to Coast april 24,2016 mp3

In the first half, UFO expert, Robert Hastings joins George Knapp to discuss his more than 150 interviews with US Air Force veterans who were involved in one or more incidents which confirm that UFO incursions at nuclear weapons sites occurred as early as 1945, even before the end of World War II. Followed by NDE expert Diane Corcoran, R.N., Ph.D., who'll talk about people's Near Death Experiences, and how the aftermath is often fraught with challenges not only for the experiencers, but the professionals who care for them.
